description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint a library assistant who is passionate about providing Library and Knowledge Services to staff, students, patients, carers and volunteers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join the Lancashire &amp; South Cumbria NHS Foundation Trust, Gosall Library team. We are looking for someone who has an innovative approach and is keen to explore new ideas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To succeed in this role you will need confidence, have a flexible approach and be able to prioritise workloads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a small, professional, friendly team, based in the Lantern Centre, Preston.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The post is advertised on a permanent basis for 19 hours per week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Carmel SmithJob - Library Manager at Carmel.Smith@lscft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
